---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import BannerContainer from "../BannerContainer.astro";
import Bee from "@/assets/images/bee.png";
import Jar from "@/assets/images/frasco.jpg";
---

<article class="py-2 box-border">
  <div class="relative md:h-auto bg-banner py-14 lg:py-11 xl:py-12 2xl:py-14">
    <BannerContainer>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col gap-7 lg:gap-0 md:grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_0.9fr]"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-9 2xl:gap-9 relative">
          <h1
            class="text-primary-dark text-md md:text-sm lg:text-md 2xl:text-base font-semibold tracking-wider"
          >
            ¿PORQUÉ ELEGIR MIEL NATURAL?
          </h1>
          <!-- Linea decorativa del titulo -->
          <div
            class="absolute w-10 h-px bg-honey-500 top-8 md:top-7 2xl:top-9 left-3 md:left-3 lg:left-3 xl:left-3"
          >
          </div>
          <p
            class="text-description-dark font-extralight text-xs lg:text-sm 2xl:text-base leading-6 xl:leading-7 2xl:leading-8 mb-2 sm:mb-4 md:max-w-sm lg:max-w-md 2xl:max-w-lg"
          >
            It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by
            the readable content of a page when looking at its layout. The point
            of using Lorem Ipsum is that it has a more-or-less normal
            distribution of letters
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Imagenes -->
        <div class="w-50 md:w-auto h-0 md:h-40 self-end -mt-7 relative">
          <Image
            src={Bee}
            alt="Abeja posada sobre una flor"
            class="absolute w-34 md:w-50 lg:w-53 xl:w-64 2xl:w-72 h-34 md:h-50 lg:h-53 xl:h-64 2xl:h-72 rounded-full object-cover md:right-15 xl:right-24 2xl:right-29 md:top-7 lg:top-3 xl:-top-6 2xl:-top-14"
          />
          <div
            class="absolute p-0.5 xl:p-1 left-20 md:left-auto -bottom-37 md:-bottom-19 lg:-bottom-23 xl:-bottom-26 md:right-0 rounded-full border-2 border-dashed border-honey-500"
          >
            <Image
              src={Jar}
              alt="Frasco de vidrio con miel dentro"
              class="w-28 md:w-34 lg:w-40 xl:w-50 h-28 md:h-34 lg:h-40 xl:h-50 rounded-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </BannerContainer>
  </div>
</article>

<style>
  .bg-banner {
    background-color:;
    background: url("/hexagons.svg"), var(--color-honey-950);
  }
</style>
